Buildcoin
==========

Buildcoin is a CI game that rewards users for committing often, keeping the build stable, and using pull requests for code reviews. Your team can play with points or cash.

Install Notes
-------------

  1. Sign up at http://buildcoin.com
  2. On the Manage Company page you can find your Company API Key. Just paste it in here.
  3. Enjoy.

Developer Notes
---------------

data
  - company_key

payload
  - refer to docs/github_payload
